properties.areaDesc: Rappahannock River from Urbanna to Windmill Point; Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA; Chesapeake Bay from Windmill Point to New Point Comfort VA
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued February 2 at 7:01AM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
Automated weather sensors and web cameras indicate areas of fog
have developed across much of the Rappahannock River and the
Chesapeake Bay north of Windmill Point. Visbilities are generally
greater than 1 SM at this time, but may diminish further as we
head through mid-morning.

If you must navigate, exercise caution. Use proper fog signals.
Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use your radar
and compass.

NWSheadline: AREAS OF MARINE FOG THIS MORNING
